description: Product Description Greener Route Be Kind to our planet - its cool to be kind! Greener Route Imitation Kraft Paper Roll Pure Kraft Paper Roll In a world where environmental concerns are becoming more pronounced, it's crucial for businesses and individuals alike to make sustainable choices. Packaging materials, in particular, have a significant impact on the environment, but there is a solution that combines functionality with sustainability: Pure Kraft Paper Rolls. These versatile and eco rolls are revolutionizing the packaging industry, and in this article, we will explore why you should consider them for your packaging needs. What is Pure Kraft Paper? Pure Kraft Paper is a type of unbleached, untreated paper made from virgin wood pulp obtained from sustainably managed forests. Unlike conventional bleached paper, Pure Kraft Paper retains its natural brown colour, which adds a touch of rustic charm to the packaging. The production process involves minimal chemical treatment, ensuring that the paper remains eco from start to finish. Environment Advantages Renewable Resource: Pure Kraft Paper is sourced from responsibly managed forests where trees are continuously replanted, making it a renewable resource. By choosing this paper, you contribute to the preservation of our forests and the promotion of sustainable forestry practices. 100% Recyclable: When disposed of, Pure Kraft Paper degrades naturally, reducing its impact on landfills and the environment. Additionally, it is easily recyclable, promoting a circular economy and reducing the demand for new raw materials. Lower Carbon Footprint: The manufacturing process of Pure Kraft Paper requires less energy and produces fewer greenhouse gas emissions compared to bleached paper and plastic alternatives, making it a greener choice for your packaging needs. Versatility in Packaging Gift Wrapping: Adds elegance and simplicity to gifts, showcasing eco-consciousness. Whether it's for personal gifts or corporate giveaways, using Kraft Paper showcases your commitment to eco-conscious practices. Shipping and Postal Needs: Provides secure packaging and void fill material. Art and Craft Projects: Ideal for creative projects, with a beautiful texture and color. Sustainable Merchandising: Eco packaging for products appeals to conscious consumers. In addition to its eco qualities, Pure Kraft Paper can also enhance your branding efforts: Customization: Kraft Paper can be easily customized with printing or stamping, allowing you to add your logo, tagline, or other branding elements. This personal touch creates a memorable unboxing experience for your customers. Storytelling: Leveraging the eco-friendliness of Kraft Paper in your branding narrative helps communicate your brand's values, ethics, and dedication to preserving the environment. Greener Route, be kind to our planet, its cool to be kind. GreenerRoute is a distributor for high-quality sustainable, natural products We are committed to doing the least harm to the environment We are committed to a zero waste plastic free practices All products are manufactured responsibly, ethically and are vegan Products using plastics (such as eco household cleaning products) are doing so as technology has not yet found alternatives. The plastics they used are from recycled plastics and are fully recyclable with no ink contamination. We always try to source our products from UK manufacturers or UK suppliers - Failing that, we source as geographically close to the UK as possible to minimise our CO2 impact. We are always actively searching for greener innovations and solutions Our packaging is from sustainable or recycled resources. 100% of the packaging we use is recyclable (*when Greener Route fulfils the order)
